	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Ristar|href=/861M)
	" and 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Rocket Knight Adventures|href=/958M)
	". Rocket Knight in particular had been on the cue for improvement for a long while. In addition to this, he added many features to the Gens emulator so it was as easy to use as the other emulators on the site. Highlights for Upthorn on Genesis in 2007: 
