[div class=p 
	"History: The N64 was dominated by Super Mario 64 in 2007. While there were other good and popular runs up for the award, such as 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Goldeneye|href=/1007M)
	" and 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Majora's Mask|href=/963M)
	", the uncontested winner for the category was 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=0 star Super Mario 64|href=/1017M)
